{"tid":1029322,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人成日話 投資係致富途徑，到我想出錢投資又比佢地鬧","createTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T12:01:40.000Z","uid":35361,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a79d4d2ca74277fcdc499b6cb46f032716f79d3","tid":1029322,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"本身有打開機，而且都打得唔錯, 平時係yahoo email我個簽名title都係叫做電競師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁做得電競師，就好似運動員咁需要日日訓練，所以係要日日打機keep住個狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我部電腦都用左3年，呢排打機開始Lag機，有時仲因為我Lag機搞到比對手團滅，隊友都話咁落去一定比我雷死場場輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我都視電競師為我未來發展既職業，要發展得好就要有一定既投資，所以我就同老豆傾 想佢比D錢我投資一下我D電競裝備，買部新電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我比左條list我老豆 叫佢去黃金砌返黎比我，因為我要keep住訓練 唔得閒自己去砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.terminalhk.com/pcSystem/customize/59f82f314d6b53aa04f21b69\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.terminalhk.com%2FpcSystem%2Fcustomize%2F59f82f314d6b53aa04f21b69&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n86EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=26fa0b87\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.terminalhk.com/pcSystem/customize/59f82f314d6b53aa04f21b69</a><br />\n佢睇完之後依依哦哦話乜成萬二銀 又話依家果部唔用得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌! 我即刻開佢波，佢都唔知電競師搵成幾百萬年薪，依家投資果一萬幾千，將來回報過百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢視野咁窄，又唔睇長遠回報，到時我搵到錢一定唔會比錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6778dd099528f60e87cc6cfd732625c49ac8db20","tid":1029322,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:11:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e07968f4b94b6e397e9378f1db87f34efd026ca9","tid":1029322,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001dd8524201330d3feb86e286d2e015794789a0","tid":1029322,"uid":236517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cc542ff0dc81299cdd26be23084772ac4f920f3","tid":1029322,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001dd8524201330d3feb86e286d2e015794789a0","tid":1029322,"uid":236517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"要訓練電競 冇時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff2ab2c186d74aabcad3b2759cd2332238e792c","tid":1029322,"uid":227581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"樓主成日話 投資係致富途徑 到連登仔要樓主停打一個月去番工 樓主又唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}